About this item

  • Creat for EntertainmentRGB effects with 213 preset modes,bring your entertainment movies sports songs and gaming to life, you'll be immersed in your favorite movies, games, or songs with a vibrant light show, enhance your gaming, movie and music experience.
  • Music synchronization modeWith the built-in microphone, the smart light bars syncs smoothly with your music or ambient sound, the light can react and move to the beat of your music, movie, and gaming audio for an immersive sound and light experience like no other, perfect for setting the mood for a family concert, karaoke night or gaming, etc.
  • 3 Control MethodsEasily manage your light bars with the APP, remote control or control box,Customize the exact light you want , Control segmented color and brightness.Also, you can DIY color, set up music sync and scene mode.
  • Timing Function You can set the light to turn on and off at your preferred time, allows you to fall asleep or wake up in a warm atmosphere.And you don't need to worry about forgetting to turn them off when you leave the house, very convenient for you to use it in your daily life.
  • Safe&High QualityThe smart light bars is made of alloy,plastic,electronic components material,durable and long-lasting,sturdy,it has extremely low heat, so children and pets can touch it with confidence. Dual design of anti-skid and counterweight for more stable use. We provide professional customer service before and after purchase. If there is any quality issue with the light bars, please feel free to contact us.

How customer reviews and ratings work

Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

    I wish the cord was longer (you have to put both lamps in one cord)

    The app doesn't let you make your own patterns which is sad. You also can't pick which colors it uses in the patterns which is sad.

    You can't do two different colors on the two lamps.

    These are only really good for sitting in the stand. Hanging them on the wall is kind of janky because the cords stick out the back. You also can't really hang them on the ceiling so don't get any ideas.

    I used the provided adhesive; we will see how long the two little stickies last for two lamps.
